Title: Wipe Away Their Smiles
Description:
The kobyss grow bold if they feel they can defile our Veneration Grounds. I think we should collect their teeth to wipe the smiles off their faces.

Come! My brother and I will cleanse our lands from this filth. Try to keep up!
ObjectivesText: Collect kobyss teeth from slain kobyss.
RewardText:
A job well done, I think.

And you managed to keep up!
